  "code": "%% DistributedShoppingStore – Sequence: Cached Item List with ETag\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant U as Client\n    participant API as REST API\n    participant C as Cache\n    participant S as Trading Service\n    participant D as Database\n\n    U->>API: GET /rooms/roomId/items with If-None-Match header\n    API->>C: GET room:roomId:items\n    alt Cache hit and ETag matches\n        C-->>API: items + etag\n        API-->>U: 304 Not Modified\n    else Cache miss or stale\n        API->>S: GetItems(roomId)\n        S->>D: SELECT items WHERE roomId\n        D-->>S: rows\n        S-->>API: items, version\n        API->>C: SET room:roomId:items with TTL\n        API-->>U: 200 OK items with ETag header\n    end",
  "diagram_type": "sequence size:600..900",
  "collected_at": "2026-02-27T04:26:22.878009",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个分布式购物系统的缓存流程，核心场景是客户端获取房间商品列表。关键点是引入ETag做乐观缓存，避免重复传输数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Cache",
        "ETag",
        "items"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那我理解参与者应该有Client、REST API、Cache、Trading Service和Database这五个？Client先请求API，API再查Cache？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "REST API",
        "Cache",
        "Trading Service",
        "Database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但注意Client发请求时要带上If-None-Match头，里面放ETag。API收到后先用roomId去Cache里查，key设计成room:roomId:items这种格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "REST API",
        "Cache",
        "If-None-Match",
        "roomId",
        "room:roomId:items"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把主流程画出来：Client GET /rooms/roomId/items带header，然后API去Cache GET那个key。接下来是不是要分两种情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "REST API",
        "Cache",
        "GET /rooms/roomId/items",
        "If-None-Match"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，用alt分支。第一种是Cache命中且ETag匹配，Cache直接返回items和etag给API，API回304 Not Modified给Client。第二种是Cache没命中或者数据过期。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cache",
        "ETag",
        "304 Not Modified",
        "Cache miss"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "第二种情况我走一遍：API调用Trading Service的GetItems(roomId)，Service去Database做SELECT，拿到rows后返回items和version给API。然后API要写Cache并带TTL，最后回200给Client带ETag头？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "Trading Service",
        "Database",
        "GetItems",
        "SELECT",
        "SET",
        "TTL",
        "200 OK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。version就是用来生成ETag的，SET的时候把items和TTL都存好。这样整个缓存失效和更新的闭环就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "version",
        "ETag",
        "SET",
        "TTL",
        "items"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "搞定了，我检查下：两个分支都齐了，Cache hit走304，Cache miss走200并回填Cache。所有参与者和消息流向都对应上了。",
